name: Time is part of life
description:
To live a good life sometimes it's kinda knotty, so we need to see  different form of time in life to overcome the knottiness.

This piece was made by hand drawing technique using just pen, then i give a little bit of editing through photoshop. The red part in the middle is a sand watch that represent time. While the flowers that grow all around, it represent the time that passes uncontrollably.
